primary.context: Customer has never logged in before and needs a registration link
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller and sent a Clubhouse registration link after updating the contact information for the delivery.

steps: Caller requested help logging into their account.
Agent performed account lookup and identity verification.
Agent identified that the caller needed a new registration link.
Agent confirmed contact details and corrected the email and phone number per user input.
Agent confirmed sending the Clubhouse registration link.
Caller confirmed the agent was helpful and ended the call.

clarifications.note: Agent proactively confirmed contact info before sending link

corrections.note: User corrected outdated email and phone number

actions.detail: Verified name and state of residence
Sent registration link to updated email

insights.summary: The customer wanted to set up their online owner account for the first time. The agent successfully verified the user, corrected their contact information, and sent the registration link.
